"7016A0510008" and "V-1.00" is silkscreened on the board in the FCC photos. The same text is found on the boards of the [[EnGenius EAP300]] and [[EnGenius EAP150]]. :The Wi-Fi radio is using two '''RFMD''' RF5602 power amplifier ICs.
Default settings are per the FCC manual. They may not be 100% accurate.
The power adapter shown in the FCC external photos is a '''DVE''' DSA-12G-12 FUS 120120 (100-240VAC ~ 50/60Hz, 0.3A -> 12VDC, 1A).
